      "content": "but its not that deep, i can see the fat layer but it's not gushing or anything, just a slow ooze. i'm really trying to avoid the ER. if i use the honey and then just put a really tight pressure bandage over it to keep the edges together, isn't that basically the same as getting a couple of stitches? surely it's better than just leaving it open and risking it getting dirty.",
